ay (9:45 am – 4:15 pm)Saturday (10:00 am – 4:00 pm)Sunday (12:00 pm - 4:00 pm)Pay rate: $19.75 per hour A satisfactory Police Information Check is required before beginning employment.How to applyFull job description here.Application deadline May 31, 2023 at 5:00 pm.Submit your cover letter and resume by email to Tina Nielsen, Chief Librarian info@bowenlibrary.caWe thank all applicants for their interest; however, only short-listed candidates will be contacted. Compensation $19.75 hr Closes: 31 May, 2023 Bowen Island Public Library Bowen Island , BC Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
