he ages of 16-30.To apply, please submit your cover letter and resume by June 1, 2023 to jobs@wpl.ca. Compensation 27.15/hour Closes: 1 June, 2023 Waterloo Public Library Waterloo , ON Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
